TINE is not ETL

Usage:
  tine [command] [flags] [args]
  tine [command]

Available Commands:
  run         Run tine pipelines from the specified one or more files
  graph       Generate a graph of the pipeline
  list        List all plugins
  version     Print the version number of TINE
  help        Help about any command

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for tine

Use "tine [command] --help" for more information about a command.
